I"<h2 id="solution">Solution:</h2>

<p>Assuming $n = m^k$ for some $k \geq 1$, we have</p>

\[\begin{align*}
        S(n) &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)S\left(\frac{n}{m}\right) + O(mn) \\
        &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m)S\left(\frac{n}{m^2}\right) + O(mn) \right] + O(mn) \\
        &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m) + S\left(\frac{n}{m^3}\right) + O(mn) \right] + O(mn) \right] + O(mn) \\
        &amp;\vdots \\
        &amp;\leq (cm\log_2(m))^kS(1) + (cm\log_2(m))^k
    \end{align*}\]

\[\qed\]
